Minification: 
Using node with requirejs and r.js, optimize all player .js and .css files into a single minified file.
Here are links for reference. 
node installer https://nodejs.org/en/download/
information about optimizing with requirejs http://requirejs.org/docs/optimization.html
directions on how to setup r.js http://www.svlada.com/require-js-optimization-part2/